1
00:00:02,536 --> 00:00:04,904
[YOUNG WOMAN] (ah!)
I think I drank too much!

2
00:00:05,004 --> 00:00:07,471
Well, I should
probably get going.

3
00:00:09,037 --> 00:00:11,271
[YOUNG WOMAN]
(uh...) Now, hold on!

4
00:00:11,371 --> 00:00:13,804
What's the big rush, huh?
Sit down.

5
00:00:13,904 --> 00:00:17,237
Hey, y'know, you're a lot
cuter than Shiro said.

6
00:00:17,337 --> 00:00:19,204
[KATO] You're embarrassing me.
(chuckles)

7
00:00:19,304 --> 00:00:21,704
[YOUNG WOMAN] Ha‐ha, I mean it,
seriously.

8
00:00:21,804 --> 00:00:24,537
Have you heard about
that hair thingy?

9
00:00:24,637 --> 00:00:26,037
Hold still...

10
00:00:26,137 --> 00:00:30,571
(laughs) Sorry about that!
I pulled out three by acci‐
(huh?)

11
00:00:41,704 --> 00:00:43,237
No...

12
00:00:43,337 --> 00:00:45,004
This is awkward.

13
00:00:45,104 --> 00:00:46,604
(thwack!)

14
00:00:49,971 --> 00:00:51,804
(bushes rustling)

15
00:00:58,704 --> 00:01:01,037
It was the hair
that gave me away.

16
00:01:01,137 --> 00:01:02,504
I could use some help.

17
00:01:02,604 --> 00:01:06,171
I don't normally eat meat
containing alcohol.

18
00:01:07,771 --> 00:01:09,904
(wet slurping)

19
